Say '''Lubao''' ([[salitan Kapampangan|Kapampangan]]: ''Balen ning Rubaw''), sakey baley diad [[Filipinas|Pilipino]] ed luyag na [[Pampanga]]. Onong ed [[2000]] census, walay population to ya 125,699 ya too diad 23,446 ya pamilya. Kidala an baley daridan ed saray [[kanen]], [[tobo]], [[esda]] tan [[sampaquita]] kila nia.

Karagayan nina sigud ya pangulo ni [[Dionysus Macapagal]] tan presente diad pangulo ni [[Gloria Macapagal-Arroyo]] say saray kidalan ya too kila bangon dia.


